<p>내맘대로 사이드 프로젝트는 내맘대로니까 의식의 흐름대로 막씀. 반말로 씀.</p>
<h2 id="0.-&#45236;&#47576;&#45824;&#47196;-&#45684;&#49828;-&#44592;&#49324;-&#50836;&#50557;-+-&#53328;&#47112;&#51060;&#49496;-&#54532;&#47196;&#51229;&#53944;-&#49884;&#51089;.">0. &#45236;&#47576;&#45824;&#47196; &#45684;&#49828; &#44592;&#49324; &#50836;&#50557; + &#53328;&#47112;&#51060;&#49496; &#54532;&#47196;&#51229;&#53944; &#49884;&#51089;.<a class="anchor-link" href="#0.-&#45236;&#47576;&#45824;&#47196;-&#45684;&#49828;-&#44592;&#49324;-&#50836;&#50557;-+-&#53328;&#47112;&#51060;&#49496;-&#54532;&#47196;&#51229;&#53944;-&#49884;&#51089;."> </a></h2><p>일요일 오후 1:30분.. 글쓰기 마감일인데, 이번주도 한 글자도 안썼다...</p>
<p>집에서는 안되겠다 싶어 노트북을 챙겨서 빽다방에 나왔다.</p>
<p>이번주는 <del>또 어떻게 때우나</del> 어떤 글을 써볼까 고민하다가, 사이드 프로젝트 아이디어 리스트에 고이고이 묶혀둔 <strong>뉴스 기사 요약 + 큐레이션 프로젝트</strong> 를 꺼내기로 했다. (이걸로 한 세개는 써야겠다.)</p>
<p>오래된 주제라 참고해볼 자료도 많고, 써볼 수 있는 방법들도 다양할 것 같아 공부용으로 시작해볼 괜찮은 주제 같아 사이드 프로젝트로 선정해보았다.</p>
<p>최종 결과물이 어떤 형태일 지는 아직 모르겠지만 일단 시작.</p>

<h2 id="1.-&#45936;&#51060;&#53552;-&#49688;&#51665;:-&#45684;&#49828;-&#44592;&#49324;&#47484;-&#44545;&#50612;&#48372;&#51088;">1. &#45936;&#51060;&#53552; &#49688;&#51665;: &#45684;&#49828; &#44592;&#49324;&#47484; &#44545;&#50612;&#48372;&#51088;<a class="anchor-link" href="#1.-&#45936;&#51060;&#53552;-&#49688;&#51665;:-&#45684;&#49828;-&#44592;&#49324;&#47484;-&#44545;&#50612;&#48372;&#51088;"> </a></h2><p>일단 처음엔 쉽게 접근하기 위해 <del>만만한</del> 각 언론사별 뉴스 기사들을 잘 제공하고 있는 네이버 뉴스 서비스를 털어보기로 했다.</p>
<p>네이버 뉴스 서비스를 들어가보았다.</p>
<p><img src="https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/16538186/80298237-35d9e180-87c5-11ea-920a-f945877f7649.png" alt=""></p>
<p>일단 모든 뉴스 기사를 수집하기 보다는 첫 시작점으로 오른쪽 란의 <code>가장 많이 본 뉴스</code> 데이터를 수집해보기로 했다.</p>
<h3 id="(1)-&#44545;&#50612;&#50732;-&#45936;&#51060;&#53552;-&#46895;&#50612;&#48372;&#44592;">(1) &#44545;&#50612;&#50732; &#45936;&#51060;&#53552; &#46895;&#50612;&#48372;&#44592;<a class="anchor-link" href="#(1)-&#44545;&#50612;&#50732;-&#45936;&#51060;&#53552;-&#46895;&#50612;&#48372;&#44592;"> </a></h3><p><img src="https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/16538186/80298314-f790f200-87c5-11ea-8354-f00af15b70ee.png" alt=""></p>
<p><code>가장 많이 본 뉴스</code> 서비스에서 이것저것 누르다보면 아래와 같이 url 구조를 쉽게 파악할 수 있다.</p>
<h4 id="&#47566;&#51060;-&#48376;-&#45684;&#49828;">&#47566;&#51060; &#48376; &#45684;&#49828;<a class="anchor-link" href="#&#47566;&#51060;-&#48376;-&#45684;&#49828;"> </a></h4><ul>
<li>url: <a href="https://news.naver.com/main/ranking/popularDay.nhn">https://news.naver.com/main/ranking/popularDay.nhn</a></li>
<li>rankingType: 섹션별인 경우 popular_day, 연령 별인 경우 age</li>
<li>sectionId: 102 (100: 정치, 101: 경제, 102: 사회, 103: 생활/문화, 104: 세계, 105: IT/과학, 003: 포토, 115: TV - 섹션별인 경우 사용가능)</li>
<li>subType: 30 (10대~60대) (연령 별인 경우 사용가능)</li>
<li>date: 20200426 (날짜 <code>%Y%m%d</code>) </li>
</ul>
<p><del>url 파라미터 구조가 좀 요상해보이는 건 기분탓이겠지.</del></p>
<h4 id="&#45843;&#44544;-&#47566;&#51008;-&#45684;&#49828;">&#45843;&#44544; &#47566;&#51008; &#45684;&#49828;<a class="anchor-link" href="#&#45843;&#44544;-&#47566;&#51008;-&#45684;&#49828;"> </a></h4><ul>
<li>url: <a href="https://news.naver.com/main/ranking/popularMemo.nhn">https://news.naver.com/main/ranking/popularMemo.nhn</a></li>
<li>rankingType: popular_memo</li>
<li>sectionId: 102 (100: 정치, 101: 경제, 102: 사회, 103: 생활/문화, 104: 세계, 105: IT/과학, 003: 포토, 115: TV)</li>
<li>date: 날짜 (날짜 <code>%Y%m%d</code>) </li>

<h4 id="&#44277;&#44048;-&#47566;&#51008;-&#45684;&#49828;">&#44277;&#44048; &#47566;&#51008; &#45684;&#49828;<a class="anchor-link" href="#&#44277;&#44048;-&#47566;&#51008;-&#45684;&#49828;"> </a></h4><ul>
<li>url: <a href="https://news.naver.com/main/ranking/popularLike.nhn">https://news.naver.com/main/ranking/popularLike.nhn</a></li>
<li>subType: 30 (10대~60대)</li>
<li>날짜별로는 제공하지 않는다.</li>
</ul>
<h4 id="SNS-&#44277;&#50976;-&#47566;&#51008;-&#45684;&#49828;">SNS &#44277;&#50976; &#47566;&#51008; &#45684;&#49828;<a class="anchor-link" href="#SNS-&#44277;&#50976;-&#47566;&#51008;-&#45684;&#49828;"> </a></h4><ul>
<li>url: <a href="https://news.naver.com/main/ranking/popularShare.nhn">https://news.naver.com/main/ranking/popularShare.nhn</a></li>
<li>날짜별로는 제공하지 않는다.</li>
</ul>
<p>많이 본 뉴스와 댓글 많은 뉴스의 경우 날짜 별 데이터를 긁어올 수 있었는데, 공감 많은 뉴스와 SNS 공유 많은 뉴스는 그렇지 않았다.</p>
<p>SNS 공유 많은 뉴스의 경우는 남들에게 적극적으로 공유하는 기준이라 좀 더 중요도가 높은 뉴스가 많을 것 같은데 아쉽다.</p>
<p>일단은 <code>많이 본 뉴스</code> 에 대해서 일자별 섹션별로 데이터를 크롤링해보기로 했다.</p>
<h3 id="(2)-&#44545;&#50612;&#50732;-&#45936;&#51060;&#53552;&#51032;-DOM-&#44396;&#51312;&#47484;-&#49332;&#54196;&#48376;&#45796;.">(2) &#44545;&#50612;&#50732; &#45936;&#51060;&#53552;&#51032; DOM &#44396;&#51312;&#47484; &#49332;&#54196;&#48376;&#45796;.<a class="anchor-link" href="#(2)-&#44545;&#50612;&#50732;-&#45936;&#51060;&#53552;&#51032;-DOM-&#44396;&#51312;&#47484;-&#49332;&#54196;&#48376;&#45796;."> </a></h3><p><img src="https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/16538186/80308235-b40ba780-8808-11ea-9082-957b96dd7c36.png" alt=""></p>
<p>다행히 크게 어렵지 않을 것 같이 생겼다.</p>
<p><code>ranking_list</code> 별로 <code>ranking_headline</code>, <code>ranking_lede</code>, <code>ranking_office</code>, <code>ranking_view</code> 값들을 가져오면 될 것 같다.</p>
<p><code>ranking_headline</code> 에는 해당 기사에 대한 링크도 제공하고 있어서 뉴스 내용까지 긁어올 수 있을 것 같다.</p>

</div>

<h3 id="(3)-&#53356;&#47204;&#47553;-&#53076;&#46300;-&#51089;&#49457;">(3) &#53356;&#47204;&#47553; &#53076;&#46300; &#51089;&#49457;<a class="anchor-link" href="#(3)-&#53356;&#47204;&#47553;-&#53076;&#46300;-&#51089;&#49457;"> </a></h3><p>(이하 자세한 설명은 생략한다)</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre><span></span><span class="kn">from</span> <span class="nn">datetime</span> <span class="kn">import</span> <span class="n">datetime</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">timedelta</span>

<span class="kn">from</span> <span class="nn">selenium</span> <span class="kn">import</span> <span class="n">webdriver</span>

<span class="kn">from</span> <span class="nn">tqdm</span> <span class="kn">import</span> <span class="n">tqdm</span>


<span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">get_chrome_driver</span><span class="p">():</span>
    <span class="n">chrome_options</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">webdriver</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">ChromeOptions</span><span class="p">()</span>
    <span class="n">chrome_options</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">add_argument</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s1">&#39;--headless&#39;</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="n">chrome_options</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">add_argument</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s1">&#39;--no-sandbox&#39;</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="n">chrome_options</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">add_argument</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s1">&#39;--disable-dev-shm-usage&#39;</span><span class="p">)</span>

    <span class="n">chrome_driver</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">webdriver</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Chrome</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s1">&#39;./chromedriver&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">options</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">chrome_options</span><span class="p">)</span>

    <span class="k">return</span> <span class="n">chrome_driver</span>


<span class="n">_SECTIONS</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">{</span>
    <span class="s1">&#39;100&#39;</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="s1">&#39;정치&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span>
    <span class="s1">&#39;101&#39;</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="s1">&#39;경제&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span>
    <span class="s1">&#39;102&#39;</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="s1">&#39;사회&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span>
    <span class="s1">&#39;103&#39;</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="s1">&#39;생활/문화&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span>
    <span class="s1">&#39;104&#39;</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="s1">&#39;세계&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span>
    <span class="s1">&#39;105&#39;</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="s1">&#39;IT/과학&#39;</span>
<span class="p">}</span>


<span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">get_popular_day_news_contents</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">date</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">section_id</span><span class="p">):</span>
    <span class="n">url</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="sa">f</span><span class="s1">&#39;https://news.naver.com/main/ranking/popularDay.nhn&#39;</span> \
        <span class="sa">f</span><span class="s1">&#39;?rankingType=popular_day&#39;</span> \
        <span class="sa">f</span><span class="s1">&#39;&amp;sectionId=</span><span class="si">{</span><span class="n">section_id</span><span class="si">}</span><span class="s1">&amp;date=</span><span class="si">{</span><span class="n">date</span><span class="si">}</span><span class="s1">&#39;</span>
    <span class="n">driver</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">get</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">url</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="n">driver</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">implicitly_wait</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">)</span>

    <span class="n">ranking</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">driver</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">find_elements_by_class_name</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s1">&#39;ranking&#39;</span><span class="p">)</span>

    <span class="k">if</span> <span class="n">ranking</span><span class="p">:</span>
        <span class="n">headlines</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">ranking</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">find_elements_by_class_name</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s1">&#39;ranking_headline&#39;</span><span class="p">)</span>
        <span class="n">ledes</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">ranking</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">find_elements_by_class_name</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s1">&#39;ranking_lede&#39;</span><span class="p">)</span>
        <span class="n">offices</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">ranking</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">find_elements_by_class_name</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s1">&#39;ranking_office&#39;</span><span class="p">)</span>
        <span class="n">views</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">ranking</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">find_elements_by_class_name</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s1">&#39;ranking_view&#39;</span><span class="p">)</span>

        <span class="k">return</span> <span class="nb">zip</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">headlines</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">ledes</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">offices</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">views</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="k">else</span><span class="p">:</span>
        <span class="k">return</span> <span class="kc">None</span>


<span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">get_popular_day_news</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">driver</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">start_date</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">end_date</span><span class="p">):</span>
    <span class="n">fp</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nb">open</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="sa">f</span><span class="s1">&#39;./popularDay-</span><span class="si">{</span><span class="n">start_date</span><span class="si">}</span><span class="s1">-</span><span class="si">{</span><span class="n">end_date</span><span class="si">}</span><span class="s1">.tsv&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s1">&#39;w&#39;</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="n">columns</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="s1">&#39;date&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s1">&#39;section&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s1">&#39;office&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s1">&#39;view&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s1">&#39;headline&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s1">&#39;lede&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s1">&#39;link&#39;</span><span class="p">]</span>
    <span class="n">fp</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">write</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s1">&#39;</span><span class="se">\t</span><span class="s1">&#39;</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">join</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">columns</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="s1">&#39;</span><span class="se">\n</span><span class="s1">&#39;</span><span class="p">)</span>

    <span class="n">target_dates</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">get_date_strings</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">start_date</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">end_date</span><span class="p">)</span>

    <span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">date_str</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="n">tqdm</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">target_dates</span><span class="p">):</span>
        <span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">section_id</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">section_name</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="n">_SECTIONS</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">items</span><span class="p">():</span>
            <span class="n">contents</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">get_popular_day_news_contents</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">date_str</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">section_id</span><span class="p">)</span>
            <span class="k">if</span> <span class="n">contents</span><span class="p">:</span>
                <span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">headline</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">lede</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">office</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">view</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="n">contents</span><span class="p">:</span>
                    <span class="n">headline_a_tag</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">headline</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">find_element_by_tag_name</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s1">&#39;a&#39;</span><span class="p">)</span>
                    <span class="n">contents</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s1">&#39;</span><span class="se">\t</span><span class="s1">&#39;</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">join</span><span class="p">([</span>
                        <span class="n">date_str</span><span class="p">,</span>
                        <span class="n">section_name</span><span class="p">,</span>
                        <span class="n">office</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">text</span><span class="p">,</span>
                        <span class="n">view</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">text</span><span class="p">,</span>
                        <span class="n">headline_a_tag</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">get_attribute</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s1">&#39;title&#39;</span><span class="p">),</span>
                        <span class="n">lede</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">text</span><span class="p">,</span>
                        <span class="n">headline_a_tag</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">get_attribute</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s1">&#39;href&#39;</span><span class="p">)</span>
                    <span class="p">])</span>
                    <span class="n">fp</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">write</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">contents</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="s1">&#39;</span><span class="se">\n</span><span class="s1">&#39;</span><span class="p">)</span>

    <span class="n">driver</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">quit</span><span class="p">()</span>


<span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">get_date_strings</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">start_date</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">end_date</span><span class="p">):</span>
    <span class="n">date_strings</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">[]</span>
    <span class="n">curr</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">datetime</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">strptime</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">start_date</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s1">&#39;%Y%m</span><span class="si">%d</span><span class="s1">&#39;</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="n">end</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">datetime</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">strptime</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">end_date</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s1">&#39;%Y%m</span><span class="si">%d</span><span class="s1">&#39;</span><span class="p">)</span>

    <span class="k">while</span> <span class="kc">True</span><span class="p">:</span>
        <span class="k">if</span> <span class="n">curr</span> <span class="o">&gt;</span> <span class="n">end</span><span class="p">:</span>
            <span class="k">break</span>
        <span class="k">else</span><span class="p">:</span>
            <span class="n">date_strings</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span>
                <span class="n">curr</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">strftime</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s1">&#39;%Y%m</span><span class="si">%d</span><span class="s1">&#39;</span><span class="p">)</span>
            <span class="p">)</span>
            <span class="n">curr</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">curr</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="n">timedelta</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">days</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="k">return</span> <span class="n">date_strings</span>


<span class="k">if</span> <span class="vm">__name__</span> <span class="o">==</span> <span class="s1">&#39;__main__&#39;</span><span class="p">:</span>
    <span class="n">driver</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">get_chrome_driver</span><span class="p">()</span>
    <span class="n">start_date</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s1">&#39;20200101&#39;</span>
    <span class="n">end_date</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s1">&#39;20200131&#39;</span>

    <span class="n">date_strings</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">get_date_strings</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">start_date</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">end_date</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="nb">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">date_strings</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="n">get_popular_day_news</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">driver</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">start_date</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">end_date</span><span class="p">)</span>
</pre></div>
<p>빠르게 코드를 작성하고 <code>2020년 1월</code> ~ <code>2020년 4월</code> 치의 데이터(날짜, 섹션, 언론사, 제목, 내용, 링크, 조회수)를 긁어왔다.</p>
<p>각 뉴스의 전체 내용도 링크를 통해서 쉽게 가져올 수 있을 것 같은데, 귀찮아서 다음 todo로 남겨두었다.</p>
<p>한 세션에서 가능한 요청량이 정해져있기 때문에 한번에 너무 많은 양을 호출하면 안되고 한달치 정도씩만 가져와야한다.</p>

</div>
</div>

<h3 id="(2)-&#51452;&#50836;-&#53412;&#50892;&#46300;-&#52628;&#52636;&#54644;&#48372;&#44592;">(2) &#51452;&#50836; &#53412;&#50892;&#46300; &#52628;&#52636;&#54644;&#48372;&#44592;<a class="anchor-link" href="#(2)-&#51452;&#50836;-&#53412;&#50892;&#46300;-&#52628;&#52636;&#54644;&#48372;&#44592;"> </a></h3><p>어떤 걸 해볼까하다가 뉴스 제목(headline)과 내용(lede)을 기반으로 주요 키워드를 추출해보기로 했다.</p>
<p>뉴스데이터의 경우는 신조어가 많이 등장하는 편인데, 일반 토크나이저를 사용할 경우 신조어는 잘 인식하지 못하여 <a href="https://github.com/lovit/soynlp">soynlp</a> 라이브러리를 사용하여 추출하였다.</p>
<p>내용 중 쓸모없는 <code>특수문자</code> 및 <code>19일</code>, <code>2020년</code> 등의 <code>의미없는 날짜</code>, <code>연령대 단어</code>, <code>언론사 명</code> 들은 적절히 전처리해주었다.</p>

<span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">prep</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">sent</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="nb">str</span><span class="p">):</span>
    <span class="n">prep</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">re</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">sub</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s1">&#39;\W+&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s1">&#39; &#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">sent</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="n">prep</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">re</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">sub</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="sa">r</span><span class="s1">&#39;\d+일&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s1">&#39;&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">prep</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="n">prep</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">re</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">sub</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="sa">r</span><span class="s1">&#39;\d+년&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s1">&#39;&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">prep</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="n">prep</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">re</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">sub</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="sa">r</span><span class="s1">&#39;\d+대&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s1">&#39;&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">prep</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="k">return</span> <span class="n">prep</span>


<span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">is_office</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">word</span><span class="p">):</span>
    <span class="k">if</span> <span class="n">word</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="n">_office_list</span><span class="p">:</span>
        <span class="k">return</span> <span class="kc">True</span>
    <span class="k">else</span><span class="p">:</span>
        <span class="k">return</span> <span class="kc">False</span>


<span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">get_global_top_keywords</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">data</span><span class="p">):</span>
    <span class="n">sents</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nb">list</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">data</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s1">&#39;headline&#39;</span><span class="p">])</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="nb">list</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">data</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s1">&#39;lede&#39;</span><span class="p">])</span>
    <span class="n">prep_sents</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="n">prep</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">sent</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">sent</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="n">sents</span><span class="p">]</span>
    
    <span class="n">noun_extractor</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">LRNounExtractor_v2</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">verbose</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="kc">True</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">extract_compound</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="kc">True</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="n">noun_extractor</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">train</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">prep_sents</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="n">nouns</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">noun_extractor</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">extract</span><span class="p">()</span>
    <span class="n">top_keywords</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">[]</span>
    <span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">n</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">k</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="nb">sorted</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">nouns</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">items</span><span class="p">(),</span> <span class="n">key</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="k">lambda</span> <span class="n">x</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="n">x</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">frequency</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">reverse</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="kc">True</span><span class="p">):</span>
        <span class="k">if</span> <span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">n</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="o">&gt;=</span> <span class="mi">3</span> <span class="ow">and</span> <span class="n">k</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">frequency</span> <span class="o">&gt;=</span> <span class="mi">30</span> <span class="ow">and</span> <span class="ow">not</span> <span class="n">is_office</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">n</span><span class="p">):</span>
            <span class="n">top_keywords</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">((</span><span class="n">n</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">k</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">frequency</span><span class="p">))</span>
    <span class="k">return</span> <span class="n">top_keywords</span>
</pre></div>

    </div>
</div>
</div>

</div>
    {% endraw %}

<span class="n">top_keywords</span><span class="p">[:</span><span class="mi">50</span><span class="p">]</span>

<div class="cell border-box-sizing text_cell rendered"><div class="inner_cell">
<div class="text_cell_render border-box-sizing rendered_html">
<p>2020년 1월 ~ 4월 간 핫한 키워드는 역시 <code>코로나</code> 다.</p>
<p>중간에 선거가 있어서인지 정치 관련 키워드도 보이고, 기생충, 조주빈 등 한동안 크게 이슈화 됬던 키워드들이 뽑혔다.</p>

</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="cell border-box-sizing text_cell rendered"><div class="inner_cell">
<div class="text_cell_render border-box-sizing rendered_html">
<h3 id="(3)-&#53412;&#50892;&#46300;-&#48324;-&#49884;&#44036;&#48324;-&#53944;&#47116;&#46300;-&#48372;&#44592;">(3) &#53412;&#50892;&#46300; &#48324; &#49884;&#44036;&#48324; &#53944;&#47116;&#46300; &#48372;&#44592;<a class="anchor-link" href="#(3)-&#53412;&#50892;&#46300;-&#48324;-&#49884;&#44036;&#48324;-&#53944;&#47116;&#46300;-&#48372;&#44592;"> </a></h3><ul>
<li>주요 키워드 별로 시간대 별 기사 수를 살펴보면 재밌을 것 같아 해당 키워드를 언급한 기사를 표시하고, 날자별로 그래프를 그려보기로 했다.</li>
</ul>

</div>
</div>

        <span class="n">keyword</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">keyword</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="n">keywords</span> 
        <span class="k">if</span> <span class="n">keyword</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="n">headline</span> <span class="ow">or</span> <span class="n">keyword</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="n">lede</span>
    <span class="p">]))</span>
    <span class="k">return</span> <span class="s1">&#39;,&#39;</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">join</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">news_keywords</span><span class="p">)</span>

<div class="cell border-box-sizing text_cell rendered"><div class="inner_cell">
<div class="text_cell_render border-box-sizing rendered_html">
<p>전체 데이터셋에서 키워드를 뽑으면 코로나만 너무 많이 나올 것 같아서 월별 TOP 키워드들을 뽑아서 그래프를 그려보기로 했다.</p>

<div class="cell border-box-sizing text_cell rendered"><div class="inner_cell">
<div class="text_cell_render border-box-sizing rendered_html">
<ul>
<li>공식 병명이 코로나19로 바뀌면서 <code>우한 폐렴</code> 이라는 워딩은 2월 초 이후로 잘 안쓰이게 되었다. <code>바이러스</code>는 계속 언급된다.</li>
<li>우리나라는 <code>신천지</code> 사태 이후로 확진자가 크게 늘게 되었는데, 그 이후로 확진자가 크게 늘고 마스크 대란이 일어나면서 <code>마스크</code> 키워드가 급등한 걸 볼 수 있다.</li>
<li>요즘은 재난지원금에 대한 뉴스가 많아 <code>재난지원금</code>에 대한 뉴스가 많아지고 있는 것도 확인할 수 있다.</li>
</ul>
